Company: ${ $('New Lead Added').first().json.Company }
Website: ${ $('New Lead Added').first().json.Website }

Website Content:
${ String($('Scrape Website').first().json.data || '').slice(0, 3000) }

Recent News Headlines:
${ String($('Fetch News').first().json.data || '').slice(0, 1500) }

Write a 2-3 sentence factual summary covering: what this company does, who their customers are, and their current operational focus. Output only the summary — no labels, headers, or extra commentary.`

